{"id": 1869, "genre": 1000, "title": "你生活中曾经有过哪些本末倒置的做法？", "description": "就是那些，当代社会的买椟还珠，欢迎在评论区补充！（题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 11671, "comment_count": 42, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170824100146C0BkoEeS5IpcOAJi.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-27T17:00:38Z", "questions": [{"id": 2850, "title": "你生活中曾经有过哪些本末倒置的做法？", "content": "你生活中曾经有过哪些本末倒置的做法？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 231158, "content": "抓小放大：为了省钱，浪费许多时间成本，比如花时间转机、退税", "image": "img/option/option/20170824101749ECt0NXksx4yKAvV8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231159, "content": "为实现效率最大化，牺牲感受：比如把旅游行程排满疲于奔命", "image": "img/option/option/20170824100449Qbi5aYyeM8gmnEGu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231160, "content": "动辄“洗心革面”，频繁设置太高的目标：结果因为根本完不成而放弃", "image": "img/option/option/20170824100751yRPU16ilqQZ7oKCh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231162, "content": "用激烈而容易反弹的方法：比如断食减肥，把朋友圈关掉，卸载游戏", "image": "img/option/option/201708241018091DEo2vcwfqGBkJzK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231163, "content": "对自己的弱点认识不清：为了省钱关注折扣信息网站，结果花出去更多", "image": "img/option/option/20170824102837LK2oRDfjNXI61iTB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231164, "content": "方法走偏：为了改变人生，企图升级人际圈子提升层次，结果没啥用", "image": "img/option/option/20170824103417a6e5TziqBjbxXAwZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231165, "content": "关注点分散：找工作研究写简历，研究了很久排版字体和怎么吹牛", "image": "img/option/option/20170824104459jGOY6yw0ToQbJHFI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231166, "content": "磨刀不误砍柴工，但磨刀花很久时间：看手账制作的时间比记手账还长", "image": "img/option/option/20170824105205DAP7zwjbv1QitGyT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}